ISSUE TICKETING AND TRACKING MODUEL
user
  admin(s)
     role
        -create users
        -create projects
        -asign projects to users(project managers)
        -manages permissions
  project manager(s)
     role
       -create project modules
       -asign modules to users
       -resolve escaleted issues
  module leader(s)/developer(s)
     role
       -resolve module isues
       -escalate issues to project managers
       -assign issues to other users(i.e developers), who can solve or escalate issues to them
  
  system users/normal users/consumers
     role
       -raise issues when they arise
